msgstr "Referentiepaginalabels in marge tonen"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerpagemap.lua:430
msgid ""
"The default (★) for newly opened books that have a reference page numbers "
"map is to show reference page number labels in the margin.\n"
"\n"
"Would you like to change it?"
msgstr ""
"De standaardinstelling (★) voor ongeopende boeken die een "
"referentiepaginanummer-overzicht hebben is om referentiepaginanummers in de "
"marge te tonen.\n"
"\n"
"Deze instelling wijzigen?"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerpagemap.lua:433
msgid ""
"The default (★) for newly opened books that have a reference page numbers "
"map is to not show reference page number labels in the margin.\n"
"\n"
"Would you like to change it?"
msgstr ""
"De standaardinstelling (★) voor ongeopende boeken die een "
"referentiepaginanummer-overzicht hebben is om referentiepaginanummers niet "
"in de marge te tonen.\n"
"\n"
"Deze instelling wijzigen?"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerpagemap.lua:436
