#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerscrolling.lua:95
msgid "Scrolling"
msgstr "Scrollen"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerscrolling.lua:108
msgid "Classic scrolling"
msgstr "Klassiek scrollen"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerscrolling.lua:110
msgid "Classic scrolling will move the document with your finger."
msgstr "Bij klassiek scrollen wordt het document met de vinger verplaatst."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerscrolling.lua:123
msgid "Turbo scrolling"
msgstr "Turboscrollen"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerscrolling.lua:125
msgid ""
"Turbo scrolling will scroll the document, at each step, by the distance from "
"your initial finger position (rather than by the distance from your previous "
"finger position).\n"
"It allows for faster scrolling without the need to lift and reposition your "
"finger."
msgstr ""
"Bij turboscrollen wordt het document bij elke stap verschoven met de afstand "
"vanaf de beginpositie van de vinger (in plaats van met de afstand vanaf de "
"vorige vingerpositie).\n"
"Hierdoor is sneller scrollen mogelijk zonder de vinger op te tillen en te "
"verplaatsen."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerscrolling.lua:140
msgid "On-release scrolling"
msgstr "Scrollen bij loslaten"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerscrolling.lua:142
msgid ""
"On-release scrolling will scroll the document by the panned distance only on "
"finger up.\n"
"This is interesting on eInk if you only pan to better adjust page vertical "
"position."
msgstr ""
"Scrollen bij loslaten scrollt het document met de verschoven afstand alleen "
"bij het omhoog halen van de vinger.\n"
"Dit is interessant op eInk als het scrollen alleen dient om de verticale "
"positie van de pagina beter aan te passen."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerscrolling.lua:160
msgid "Activation delay: %1 ms"
msgstr "Activeringsvertraging: %1 ms"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerscrolling.lua:170
msgid "Scroll activation delay"
msgstr "Scroll-activeringsvertraging"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerscrolling.lua:172
msgid ""
"A delay can be used to avoid scrolling when swipes or multiswipes are "
"intended.\n"
